  316|         Deep astuple returns correct tuple.
  317|         """
  318|         assert tuple_factory(
  319|             [tuple_factory([1, 2]), tuple_factory([3, 4])]
  320|         ) == astuple(C(C(1, 2), C(3, 4)), tuple_factory=tuple_factory)
